id: The 'all' ontology for IND, North American extension, is provided for convenience for FIBO users. It imports most of the Production (Released) ontologies that comprise the FIBO Foundations (FND), Business Entities (BE), Financial Business and Commerce (FBC), and Indices and Indicators (IND) domains, excluding European individuals for governments and jurisdictions, financial services, regulatory organizations and related registries, and reference individuals.

id: The FIBO Indices and Indicators (IND) Domain covers market indices and reference rates including economic indicators, foreign exchange, interest rates, and other benchmarks. The ontologies cover quoted interest rates, economic measures such as employment rates, and quoted indices required to support baskets of securities, including specific kinds of securities in share indices or bond indices, as well as credit indices.
